reviewText:
love Eamonn  McCrytal's music
love to see him come to Melbourne Florida USA for a concert
Very good show!!  Eamonn  is a great singer and his guest was great too.
I would prefer that Eamonn McCrystal ONLY perform for the entire concert. Guests talented but just wasn't what I was expecting.
Had never heard of him before. He is very good, would order more of his albums
